Adiukwu Daniel Nkemakolam ama dịka Kemzart akụwala akụoyibo nsugbe gbasara mmasị o nwere n'ọrụ ya.
O meerela ndị a ma ama dịka Zoro, Rudeboy, King Perry na Kizz Daniel ihe onyonyo.
'Ndị ohi ezuchaala ọtụtụ ihe nka Igboukwu'
E ji nka  agwọ ọrịa obi ịdamba -Ojii nka agwọ ọrịa
Ị hụtụla ebe e ji ọkụ ese ihe?
Ọ kọwara etu mmasị o nwere n'ọrụ a si duru ya bata Legọs ma na-eme ọfụma n'ọrụ aka ya.
Kirie onyonyo ya n'uju n'elu.
'Ụfọdụ akpụrakpụ ndị ọcha na-ere bụ nke ezuru n'ori'
Akuziri m onwe m iji mkpịsị odee ese ihe - Patrick Chuka
Ịrụ ụlọ ekwesịghị iri gị ego makana ihe e ji arụ ya dị n'ala - Demas Nwoko
Ị ma na onye ọbara mgbali elu na-eme n'afọ 30 na 40 nwere ike imecha nwee nsogbu n'ụbụrụ?
